text: Marcel Coppin (27 April 1928 - 17 September 2008) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics and the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:2008 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Paris
